<lb n="0185b08" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0185b09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0185b10" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"/><note n="0185001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此傳明本與宋本元本宮本對校 cf. P. 184a段</note><cb:jhead>龍樹菩薩傳</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0185b11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0185b12" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="author">姚秦三藏法師鳩摩羅什譯</byline>
<lb n="0185b13" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><p xml:id="pT50p0185b1301"><note n="0185002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（又）＋大【宮】</note><note n="0185002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，又大【宮】</note><app n="0185002"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">又大</rdg></app>師名龍樹菩薩者。出南天竺梵志種也。
<lb n="0185b14" ed="T"/>天聰奇悟事不再告。在乳<note n="0185003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">哺之＝之哺【宋】【元】</note><note n="0185003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哺之【大】，之哺【宋】【元】</note><app n="0185003"><lem wit="【大】">哺之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">之哺</rdg></app>中。聞諸梵
<lb n="0185b15" ed="T"/>志誦四韋陀典各四萬偈。偈有四十二字。
<lb n="0185b16" ed="T"/><note n="0185004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">背誦其文＝皆領其義【宮】</note><note n="0185004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">背誦其文【大】，皆領其義【宮】</note><app n="0185004"><lem wit="【大】">背誦其文</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">皆領其義</rdg></app><note n="0185005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">而領其義＝背誦其文【宮】</note><note n="0185005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而領其義【大】，背誦其文【宮】</note><app n="0185005"><lem wit="【大】">而領其義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">背誦其文</rdg></app>。弱冠馳名獨步諸
<lb n="0185b17" ed="T"/>國。世學藝能天文地理圖緯祕讖。及諸道
<lb n="0185b18" ed="T"/>術無不悉練。契友三人亦是一時之傑。相
<lb n="0185b19" ed="T"/>與議曰天下義理可以開神明悟幽旨者。吾
<lb n="0185b20" ed="T"/>等盡之矣。復欲何以自娛<note n="0185006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">騁情極欲＝騁欲極情【宮】</note><note n="0185006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">騁情極欲【大】，騁欲極情【宮】</note><app n="0185006"><lem wit="【大】">騁情極欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">騁欲極情</rdg></app>。最是
<lb n="0185b21" ed="T"/>一生之樂。然<note n="0185007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔諸〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185007"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>梵志道士勢非<note n="0185008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王公＝公王【宮】</note><note n="0185008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王公【大】，公王【宮】</note><app n="0185008"><lem wit="【大】">王公</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">公王</rdg></app>何
<lb n="0185b22" ed="T"/>由得之。唯有<note n="0185009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（隱身之術斯））＝（（術法隱身藏形其））【宮】</note><note n="0185009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">隱身之術斯【大】，術法隱身藏形其【宮】</note><app n="0185009"><lem wit="【大】">隱身之術斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">術法隱身藏形其</rdg></app>樂可辦。四人相
<lb n="0185b23" ed="T"/>視莫逆於心。俱至術家求隱身法。術師念
<lb n="0185b24" ed="T"/>曰。此四梵志<note n="0185010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">擅＝誕【宮】</note><note n="0185010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">擅【大】，誕【宮】</note><app n="0185010"><lem wit="【大】">擅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">誕</rdg></app>名一世。草芥群生今以術
<lb n="0185b25" ed="T"/>故屈辱就我。我若呪法授之。此人才明絕
<lb n="0185b26" ed="T"/>世所不知者唯此賤法。若得之便去不復
<lb n="0185b27" ed="T"/>可屈。且與其藥使日用而不知。<note n="0185011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">藥盡必＝盡則【宮】</note><note n="0185011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藥盡必【大】，盡則【宮】</note><app n="0185011"><lem wit="【大】">藥盡必</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">盡則</rdg></app>來
<lb n="0185b28" ed="T"/><note n="0185012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">求＝永【宋】【元】</note><note n="0185012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">求【大】，永【宋】【元】</note><app n="0185012"><lem wit="【大】">求</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">永</rdg></app>。<note n="0185013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（可以…子））八字＝（（當師我））三字【宋】【元】</note><note n="0185013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（可以…子）八字【大】，當師我【宋】【元】</note><app cb:word-count="8" n="0185013"><lem wit="【大】">可以術屈為我弟子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">當師我</rdg></app>。各與青藥一丸
<lb n="0185b29" ed="T"/>告之曰。汝於靜處用水磨之以塗眼瞼。則
<pb n="0185c" xml:id="T50.2047b.0185c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0185c01" ed="T"/>無有人能見汝形者。龍樹菩薩磨藥聞氣。
<lb n="0185c02" ed="T"/>便盡知藥名分數。多少<note n="0185014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔錙銖無失〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">錙銖無失【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185014"><lem wit="【大】">錙銖無失</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。隨其
<lb n="0185c03" ed="T"/>氣勢龍樹識之。還語術師此藥有七十種。
<lb n="0185c04" ed="T"/>分數多少盡<note n="0185015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">如其方＝而說之【宮】</note><note n="0185015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如其方【大】，而說之【宮】</note><app n="0185015"><lem wit="【大】">如其方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">而說之</rdg></app>。藥師問曰汝何由知。
<lb n="0185c05" ed="T"/>答曰藥自有氣何以不知。<note n="0185016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（師即…耶））二十四字＝（（師伏其神明鏡徹領識拔奇此人難遇況今願學我此術法何足祕悋））二十七字【宮】</note><note n="0185016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（師即…耶）二十四字【大】，師伏其神明鏡徹領識拔奇此人難遇況今願學我此術法何足祕悋【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="24" n="0185016"><lem wit="【大】">師即歎伏。<note n="0185017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">顧＝願【宋】【元】</note><note n="0185017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">顧【大】，願【宋】【元】</note><app n="0185017"><lem wit="【大】">顧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">願</rdg></app>
<lb n="0185c06" ed="T"/>斯人者聞之猶難。而況相學。我之賤術何
<lb n="0185c07" ed="T"/>足惜耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">師伏其神明鏡徹領識拔奇此人難遇況今願學我此術法何足祕悋</rdg></app>。即具授。<note n="0185018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">其＋（術）【宮】</note><note n="0185018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其【大】，其術【宮】</note><app n="0185018"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">其術</rdg></app>四人<note n="0185019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔得術〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得術【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185019"><lem wit="【大】">得術</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>隱身<note n="0185020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔自在〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自在【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185020"><lem wit="【大】">自在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0185c08" ed="T"/>入王宮中。宮中美人皆被侵陵百餘日。後
<lb n="0185c09" ed="T"/>宮<note n="0185021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔中人有〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中人有【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185021"><lem wit="【大】">中人有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>懷妊者以事白王。王大不悅。此
<lb n="0185c10" ed="T"/>何不祥<note n="0185022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為＝有【宮】</note><note n="0185022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為【大】，有【宮】</note><app n="0185022"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">有</rdg></app>怪乃爾。召諸智臣以謀此事。有
<lb n="0185c11" ed="T"/>舊老者言<note n="0185023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">凡如此事應＝此【宮】</note><note n="0185023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">凡如此事應【大】，此【宮】</note><app n="0185023"><lem wit="【大】">凡如此事應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">此</rdg></app>有二種。或鬼或術。
<lb n="0185c12" ed="T"/>可以細土置諸門中。令有司守之斷諸術
<lb n="0185c13" ed="T"/>者。若是術人足跡自現<note n="0185024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔可以兵除〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">可以兵除【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185024"><lem wit="【大】">可以兵除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。若其是
<lb n="0185c14" ed="T"/>鬼則無跡也。鬼可呪除人可刀殺。<note n="0185025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔備法〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">備法【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185025"><lem wit="【大】">備法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>試
<lb n="0185c15" ed="T"/>之見<note n="0185026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔四人〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">四人【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185026"><lem wit="【大】">四人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>跡。即閉諸門令數百力士。<note n="0185027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">揮刀空＝拔刀闇【宮】</note><note n="0185027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">揮刀空【大】，拔刀闇【宮】</note><app n="0185027"><lem wit="【大】">揮
<lb n="0185c16" ed="T"/>刀空</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">拔刀闇</rdg></app>斫斫殺三人。<note n="0185028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔唯有〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯有【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185028"><lem wit="【大】">唯有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>龍樹<note n="0185029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">歛＝以【宮】</note><note n="0185029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斂【大】，以【宮】</note><app n="0185029"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">斂</lem><rdg wit="【大】">歛</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">以</rdg></app>身<note n="0185030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（屏氣…側））九字＝（（依王坐王頭邊頭邊））八字【宮】</note><note n="0185030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（屏氣…側）九字【大】，依王坐王頭邊頭邊【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="9" n="0185030"><lem wit="【大】">屏氣
<lb n="0185c17" ed="T"/>依王頭側。王頭側</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">依王坐王頭邊頭邊</rdg></app>七尺刀所不至。是時始
<lb n="0185c18" ed="T"/>悟欲為苦本。厭欲心生發出家願。若我得
<lb n="0185c19" ed="T"/>脫。當詣沙門求出家法。既而得出入山詣
<lb n="0185c20" ed="T"/>佛塔出家受戒。九十日中誦三藏。<note n="0185031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔盡〕－【宮】</note><note n="0185031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0185031"><lem wit="【大】">盡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>通
<lb n="0185c21" ed="T"/>諸深義。更求諸經都無得處。雪山中深遠
<lb n="0185c22" ed="T"/>處有佛塔。塔中有一老比丘。以摩訶<note n="0185032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">衍＝乘【宮】＊</note><note n="0185032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">衍【大】＊，乘【宮】＊</note><app n="0185032"><lem wit="【大】">衍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">乘</rdg></app>經
<lb n="0185c23" ed="T"/>與之。<note n="0185033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（誦受…義））八字＝（（雖得實））三字【宮】</note><note n="0185033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（誦受…義）八字【大】，雖得實【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="8" n="0185033"><lem wit="【大】">誦受愛樂雖知實義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">雖得實</rdg></app>未得<note n="0185034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">通＝道【宮】</note><note n="0185034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">通【大】，道【宮】</note><app n="0185034"><lem wit="【大】">通</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">道</rdg></app>利。周
<lb n="0185c24" ed="T"/>遊諸國更求餘經。於閻浮提中遍求不得。
<lb n="0185c25" ed="T"/>外道<note n="0185035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">論＝諸【宮】</note><note n="0185035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">論【大】，諸【宮】</note><app n="0185035"><lem wit="【大】">論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">諸</rdg></app>師沙門<note n="0185036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">義＝豪【宮】</note><note n="0185036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">義【大】，豪【宮】</note><app n="0185036"><lem wit="【大】">義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">豪</rdg></app>宗咸皆摧伏。<note n="0185037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即起憍慢＝憍慢即起【宮】</note><note n="0185037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即起憍慢【大】，憍慢即起【宮】</note><app n="0185037"><lem wit="【大】">即起憍
<pb n="0186a" xml:id="T50.2047b.0186a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0186a01" ed="T"/>慢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">憍慢即起</rdg></app>心。自念言世界法中津塗甚多。佛經雖
<lb n="0186a02" ed="T"/>妙以理推之故未盡。未盡之中可推。而說
<lb n="0186a03" ed="T"/>之以悟後學。於理不違於事無失。斯有何
<lb n="0186a04" ed="T"/>咎。思此事已。即欲行之立師教誡更造衣
<lb n="0186a05" ed="T"/>服。<note n="0186001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">今＝合【宮】</note><note n="0186001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">今【大】，合【宮】</note><app n="0186001"><lem wit="【大】">今</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">合</rdg></app>附佛法所別為異。方欲以無所推
<lb n="0186a06" ed="T"/>屈表一切智相。擇日選時<note n="0186002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔當與…衣〕十一字－【宮】</note><note n="0186002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（當與…衣）十一字【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="11" n="0186002"><lem wit="【大】">當與諸弟子。
<lb n="0186a07" ed="T"/>受新戒著新衣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>便欲行之。獨在靜室水精
<lb n="0186a08" ed="T"/>地房。大龍菩薩見其如此。惜而愍之即接
<lb n="0186a09" ed="T"/>入海。於宮殿中開七寶藏發七寶函。以諸
<lb n="0186a10" ed="T"/>方等深奧經典無上妙法授<note n="0186003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔之龍樹〕－【宮】</note><note n="0186003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之龍樹【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0186003"><lem wit="【大】">之龍樹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。龍樹
<lb n="0186a11" ed="T"/>受讀九十日中通練甚多。其心深入體得
<lb n="0186a12" ed="T"/>實利。龍知其心而問之曰。看經遍未。答言
<lb n="0186a13" ed="T"/>汝諸函中經甚多無量不可盡也。我所讀
<lb n="0186a14" ed="T"/>者已十倍閻浮提。龍言如我宮中所有經
<lb n="0186a15" ed="T"/>典。諸處此比復不可知。龍樹即得諸經一
<lb n="0186a16" ed="T"/>箱。深入無生<note n="0186004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二【宋】</note><note n="0186004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，二【宋】</note><app n="0186004"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">二</rdg></app>忍具足。龍還送出。<note n="0186005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔時南…樹〕三百二十三字－【宮】</note><note n="0186005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（時南…樹）三百二十三字【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="323" n="0186005"><lem wit="【大】">時南
<lb n="0186a17" ed="T"/>天竺王甚邪見承事外道毀謗正法。龍樹
<lb n="0186a18" ed="T"/>菩薩為化彼故躬持赤旛在王前行。經歷
<lb n="0186a19" ed="T"/>七年王始怪問。此是何人在<note n="0186006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我＝吾【宋】【元】</note><note n="0186006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我【大】，吾【宋】【元】</note><app n="0186006"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">吾</rdg></app>前行。答曰
<lb n="0186a20" ed="T"/>我是一切智人。王聞是已甚大驚愕而問
<lb n="0186a21" ed="T"/>之言。一切智人曠代不有。汝自言是何以
<lb n="0186a22" ed="T"/>驗之。答言欲知智在說王當見問。王即自
<lb n="0186a23" ed="T"/>念我為智主大論議師。問之能屈猶不足
<lb n="0186a24" ed="T"/>名。一旦不如此非小事。若其不問便是一
<lb n="0186a25" ed="T"/>屈遲疑良久。不得已而問之。天今何為耶。
<lb n="0186a26" ed="T"/>龍樹言天今與阿脩羅戰。王聞此言譬如
<lb n="0186a27" ed="T"/>人噎。既不得吐又不得咽。欲非其言復無
<lb n="0186a28" ed="T"/>以證之。欲是其事無事可明。未言之間龍
<lb n="0186a29" ed="T"/>樹復言。此非虛論求勝之談。王小待之須
<pb n="0186b" xml:id="T50.2047b.0186b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0186b01" ed="T"/>臾有驗。言訖空中便有干戈兵器相係而
<lb n="0186b02" ed="T"/>落。王言干戈矛戟雖是戰器。汝何必知是
<lb n="0186b03" ed="T"/>天與阿脩羅戰。龍樹言搆之虛言不如校
<lb n="0186b04" ed="T"/>以實事。言已阿脩羅手足指及其耳鼻從
<lb n="0186b05" ed="T"/>空而下。又令王及臣民婆羅門眾。見空中
<lb n="0186b06" ed="T"/>清除兩陣相對。王乃稽首伏其法化。殿上
<lb n="0186b07" ed="T"/>有萬婆羅門。皆棄束髮受成就戒。是時龍
<lb n="0186b08" ed="T"/>樹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>．於南天竺大弘佛教。摧伏外道廣明摩
<lb n="0186b09" ed="T"/>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0185032"><lem wit="【大】">衍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">乘</rdg></app>。作優波提舍十萬偈。又作莊嚴佛
<lb n="0186b10" ed="T"/>道<note n="0186007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔論〕－【宮】＊</note><note n="0186007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">論【大】＊，〔－〕【宮】＊</note><app n="0186007"><lem wit="【大】">論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>五千偈。大慈方便<app type="star" corresp="#0186007"><lem wit="【大】">論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>五<note n="0186008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">十＝千【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0186008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十【大】，千【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0186008"><lem wit="【大】">十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">千</rdg></app>偈。令摩
<lb n="0186b11" ed="T"/>訶<app type="star" corresp="#0185032"><lem wit="【大】">衍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">乘</rdg></app>教大行於天竺。又造無畏論十萬偈。
<lb n="0186b12" ed="T"/>於無畏中出中論也。時有婆羅門善知呪
<lb n="0186b13" ed="T"/>術。欲以所能與龍樹諍勝告天竺國王。我
<lb n="0186b14" ed="T"/>能伏此比丘王當驗之。王言汝大愚人。此
<lb n="0186b15" ed="T"/>菩薩者明與日月爭光。智與聖<note n="0186009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心並照＝人並能【宮】</note><note n="0186009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心並照【大】，人並能【宮】</note><app n="0186009"><lem wit="【大】">心並照</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">人並能</rdg></app>。汝
<lb n="0186b16" ed="T"/>何不遜敢不推敬。婆羅門言。王為智人何
<lb n="0186b17" ed="T"/>不以理驗之。而抑斷一切。王見言至為請
<lb n="0186b18" ed="T"/>龍樹。清旦共坐政德殿上。婆羅門後至便
<lb n="0186b19" ed="T"/>於殿前呪作大池。廣長清淨中有千葉蓮
<lb n="0186b20" ed="T"/>華。自坐其上而訶龍樹。汝在地坐如畜生
<lb n="0186b21" ed="T"/>無異。而欲與我清淨<note n="0186010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔華上〕－【宮】</note><note n="0186010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">華上【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0186010"><lem wit="【大】">華上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>大<note n="0186011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">德智人＝智【宮】</note><note n="0186011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">德智人【大】，智【宮】</note><app n="0186011"><lem wit="【大】">德智人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">智</rdg></app>抗
<lb n="0186b22" ed="T"/>言論議。爾時龍樹亦以呪術化作一六牙白
<lb n="0186b23" ed="T"/>象。行池水上趣其華坐以鼻繳拔高舉擲
<lb n="0186b24" ed="T"/>地。婆羅門傷腰委頓。歸命龍樹我不自量
<lb n="0186b25" ed="T"/>毀辱大師。願哀受我啟其愚蒙。有一小乘
<lb n="0186b26" ed="T"/><note n="0186012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（法師…言））十一字＝（（道人先為法主龍樹問言））十字【宮】</note><note n="0186012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（法師…言）十一字【大】，道人先為法主龍樹問言【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="11" n="0186012"><lem wit="【大】">法師。常懷忿嫉。龍樹問之言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">道人先為法主龍樹問言</rdg></app>汝樂我久
<lb n="0186b27" ed="T"/>住世不。答言實不願也。退入閑室經日不
<lb n="0186b28" ed="T"/>出。弟子破戶看之遂蟬蛻而去。去世已來
<lb n="0186b29" ed="T"/>始<note n="0186013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔過〕－【宮】</note><note n="0186013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0186013"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>百歲。南天竺諸國。為其立廟敬奉
<pb n="0186c" xml:id="T50.2047b.0186c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0186c01" ed="T"/>如佛。其母樹下生之。因字阿周<note n="0186014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔陀〕－【宮】＊</note><note n="0186014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陀【大】＊，〔－〕【宮】＊</note><app n="0186014"><lem wit="【大】">陀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>那。阿
<lb n="0186c02" ed="T"/>周<app type="star" corresp="#0186014"><lem wit="【大】">陀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>那樹名也。以龍成其道故以龍<note n="0186015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔配〕－【宮】</note><note n="0186015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">配【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0186015"><lem wit="【大】">配</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0186c03" ed="T"/>字號曰龍<note n="0186016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔樹〕－【宮】</note><note n="0186016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">樹【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0186016"><lem wit="【大】">樹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>也<note n="0186017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔依付…法〕十八字－【宮】</note><note n="0186017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（依付…法）十八字【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="18" n="0186017"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">依付法藏經即第十三祖三百餘年任持<note n="0186018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛法＋（其所）【宋】</note><note n="0186018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛法【大】，佛法其所【宋】</note><app n="0186018"><lem wit="【大】">佛法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">佛法其所</rdg></app></note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0186c04" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>龍樹菩薩傳<note n="0186019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔終〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0186019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">終【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0186019"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">終</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
